# Summary
The Amplitude Activation Braze streaming integration enables real-time forwarding of Amplitude events and user data to Braze, requiring Braze API Endpoint, API Key, and App ID for setup. It supports bidirectional data flow, user identification via External ID/Braze ID/User Alias/Email, and selective event and user property forwarding.

